snippet.textDisplay: I am Hindu, Brahmin from India. I listened to this beautiful kalam. I do not know much of Urdu or Hindi for that matter. But, believe me this song brought tears to my eyes. This is really peaceful and beautiful. I love this. And I have been writing a lot of stuff against Pakistan, I listened to Coke Studio Meesha, Abu Ayaz, Alif Allah, Arif Lohar....I openly say no one beats our beloved neighbour Pakistan in Sufi and Coke Studio. Lot's of respect and love from India. May you keep on making such awesome songs Insha Allah! And forgive me my Pakistani friends if my comments have hurt anyone of you. Jai Hind!
